      "text": "process\n    - illusion\n    - it has ALL the RAM\n    - the processor only lives for it.\n         - it doesn't ask for time, or release the thread. \n            the scheduler does that.\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "process\n    - illusion\n    - it has ALL the RAM\n    - the processor only lives for it.\n         - it doesn't ask for time, or release the thread. \n            the scheduler does that.\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
